creator: FIBA
descriptionHtml:
Welcome to Courtside 1891. Designed to bring video and live data from professional basketball played across the globe into a single, smart destination. You can curate and choose the experience you want, so you can easily follow the sport you love from around the globe.

Max – Annual: A paid subscription giving access to live games, multiple highlight options & personalised game centre all year long for FIBA sanctioned men’s, women’s and youth events

Max – Event: A paid subscription giving access to live games & full replays running across unique FIBA sanctioned men’s, women’s and youth events

Plus - (*Free to join*): A free account giving access to extended highlights & a curated feed. No credit card required.
